 **Modern Tech Stack**: Next.js 14, Node.js, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, Redis
 **Containerization**: Docker & Docker Compose for easy deployment
 **Authentication**: JWT-based auth with secure password hashing
 **Payment Integration**: Stripe payment processing ready
 **File Storage**: MinIO for scalable file/image storage
 **Search**: Elasticsearch for powerful product search
 **Caching**: Redis for session management and caching
 **Database**: PostgreSQL with proper relationships and indexes
 **Security**: Helmet, CORS, rate limiting, input validation
 **Monitoring**: Structured logging with Winston
 **Development**: Hot reload, TypeScript, ESLint
 **Production Ready**: Nginx reverse proxy, SSL ready